Package craterdog.collections.abstractions

Class Sorter<E>

java.lang.Object
craterdog.collections.abstractions.Sorter<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of element being sorted.
Direct Known Subclasses:
MergeSorter, RandomSorter
public abstract class Sorter<E> extends Object
This abstract class defines a framework for each concrete sorter class that sorts the elements in a collection using a specific algorithm and comparator function.
Author:
Derk Norton
